reviews.review_text: smooth real smooth 76-06 going here, smooth is just the perfect word, and lucid, nothing on fire but just pure water here, high quality

Smooth is the word! Great quality recording. Totally agree with gratedude69 about smooth. Comes from Jer's TB1000A. Does not cut through the traffic like the TB500 or Wolf but it rings like bells from heaven. This is a special period of time for a variety of other reasons but there were only 26 GD concerts with the TB1000A and only three before the first Boston concert on June 9.
Searching For The Sound Well played show with fantastic Sound.Dig In,It's High Time For Some 1976 Grateful Dead
